These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, july, may, february
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, satire
House: art-deco, modern, palace, craftsman
1. the art-deco house is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the palace house is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
4. the modern house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
6. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
8. the craftsman house is between the person watching satire movies and the person who's birthday is in january##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Birthday         | february      | january | july | may |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime  | drama   | satire    |
| House     | art-deco     | palace    | craftsman    | modern      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
City: liverpool, paris, nizza, venice
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, mexican, polish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, swimming, rowing, climbing
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
2. the person traveling to venice is the mexican##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the japanese##1
7. the american is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to paris##2
8. the polish is between the japanese and the person traveling to nizza##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| City         | venice | nizza   | paris | liverpool  |
| Nationality   | mexican     | american | polish  | japanese |
| Sport     | climbing        | rowing  | swimming    | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, march, october, september
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, canadian, german
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, baccarat, prince, blend
1. the german is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in september##2
2. the argentine is the blend-smoker##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
6. the canadian is between the person who's birthday is in march and the american##2
7. the german is on the left of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday          | february | march   | september     | october     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german | canadian   | american  |
| Cigar     | blend      | baccarat | prince | old-henry |

