.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, january, october
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, punk, salsa, soul
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, lily, azalea, poppy
1. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who growslily##1
3. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
5. the fan of soul is the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is the fan of pop##1
7. the fan of salsa is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Birthday   | february  | october   | january     | april |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | soul      | pop        | punk     |
| Flower         | azalea | begonia | poppy | lily   |

