.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
City: nizza, london, boston, rome
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, swimming, volleyball
House: modern, victorian, cottage, wooden
1. the person traveling to rome is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4
3. the modern house is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the victorian house is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the modern house is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
7. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
9. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| City   | nizza   | rome   | boston | london |
| Sport         | rugby      | volleyball | golf      | swimming |
| House     | victorian | modern        | wooden       | cottage  |

