.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
4 different games are played: snooker, backgammon, mah-jongg, scrabble
House: futuristic, cape-cod, ranch-style, townhouse
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
6. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
7. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4
8. the townhouse house is on the right of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Game    | mah-jongg   | scrabble      | backgammon       | snooker |
| House   | futuristic | townhouse | ranch-style     | cape-cod |
| Pet     | rat     | guinea-pig  | chinchilla | hamster |

