.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, cooking, reading, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, martial-arts, satire, time-travel
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, ship, helicopter, roller
1. the person driving the helicopter is the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person driving the ship is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person driving the taxi##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby      | reading   | chess          | cooking | woodworking        |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | martial-arts | time-travel   | comedy     |
| Transport           | taxi | ship         | roller         | helicopter |

