.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, collecting, drawing, singing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, biathlon, cycling, swimming
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, drama, thriller, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person watching drama movies is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
7. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | chess      | drawing       | singing    |
| Sport           | biathlon  | cycling  | swimming | golf |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific      | thriller | drama         | superhero    |

