.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, tram, ship, trike
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, american, turkish, brazilian
1. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
4. the american is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the turkish##3
6. the brazilian is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the person driving the trike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta         | coffee  | iced-tea     | water         |
| Transport        | trike | tram | scooter | ship         |
| Nationality      | american         | turkish  | nigerian   | brazilian |

