.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, indie, punk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, zombie, western, horror
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, swisher, game, oliveros
 1. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the person watching western movies is between the fan of electronic and the fan of country##2
 5. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 6. the oliveros-smoker is the fan of indie##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of country is in an odd position##4
 9. the person watching zombie movies is between the fan of punk and the fan of indie##2
10. the game-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | country  | indie    | electronic | punk    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | western | zombie  | horror |
| Cigar           | game   | oliveros    | vegafina        | swisher   |

