.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, soy-milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, iris, rose, aconite
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, raspberry, orange, cherry
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
3. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
4. the person who growsiris is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
6. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
7. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | 7up                | soy-milk  | almond-milk | juice   |
| Flower           | aconite | iris | azalea   | rose |
| Food   | raspberry         | artichoke     | cherry     | orange |

