.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, red, apricot, blood-red
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, musical, romance, western
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, vegafina, prince, alhambra
1. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
2. the person who likes apricot is on the far left##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
4. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the davidoff-smoker is between the person watching western movies and the alhambra-smoker##2
6. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
7. the person who likes grey is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Color          | apricot    | red  | blood-red  | grey |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | action | romance |
| Cigar   | prince    | davidoff     | alhambra    | vegafina |

