.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, amaryllis, lily, poppy
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, pakistani, turkish
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, amber, ebony, chestnut
1. the person who likes amber is between the person who growslily and the argentine##2
2. the person who growssunflower is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the australian##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the pakistani is the person who growssunflower##1
9. the turkish is between the person who likes ebony and the person who likes mauve##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Flower      | sunflower | lily      | amaryllis  | poppy    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian | turkish | argentine |
| Color           | chestnut      | ebony       | amber   | mauve      |

