.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, cola, tea, hot-chocolate
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indian, indonesian, japanese
City: san-francisco, hamburg, london, rome
1. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
6. the japanese is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the australian##2
7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
8. the indian is in an even position##4
9. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage         | water    | tea | cola  | hot-chocolate  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | indian       | japanese | australian |
| City         | london   | san-francisco      | rome | hamburg       |

