.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, spanish, indonesian, indian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, mystery, satire, superhero
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, davidoff, prince, pall-mall
1. the davidoff-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the davidoff-smoker is the spanish##1
3. the spanish is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the indonesian is the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the indonesian is on the far left##1
6. the person watching family movies is the davidoff-smoker##1
7. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the indian##1
8. the pall-mall-smoker is the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Nationality      | indonesian      | spanish | american     | indian    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | family      | mystery | satire |
| Cigar           | prince   | davidoff  | old-henry     | pall-mall |

