.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, coach, pilot, writer
There 4 different types of food: plum, asparagus, apple, garlic
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car, snowmobile
1. the police-officer is on the left or right of the coach##3
2. the person eating plum is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
4. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the writer##3
5. the coach is between the person driving the bike and the person eating apple##2
6. the person driving the airplane is the person eating garlic##1
7. the coach is on the left of the police-officer##1
8. the person eating plum is on the left of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Job    | pilot    | coach     | police-officer    | writer        |
| Food       | apple   | plum | asparagus | garlic |
| Transport   | snowmobile | car      | bike    | airplane   |

