.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, february, may, august
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, disaster, spy, superhero
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, punk, disco, hip-hop
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
2. the fan of salsa is between the fan of punk and the person who's birthday is in august##2
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3
5. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of punk##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
7. the fan of disco is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's birthday is in august is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Birthday          | february | august  | january   | may    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | spy     | superhero | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | hip-hop | salsa | punk   |

