4. the person who's hobby is reading is the person eating cherry##1
5. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
6. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person eating onion##1
8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | reading   | cooking    | magic-tricks    |
| Food           | pineapple   | cherry    | cabbage | onion |
| Color   | fuchsia    | azure | yellow    | apricot         |

