.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, broccoli, lime, pomegranate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, crime, documentary, sports
City: paris, rome, prague, venice
1. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
4. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
5. the person eating broccoli is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching zombie movies##2
6. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person eating apple##1
8. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | lime    | broccoli    | apple  | pomegranate |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | crime | zombie | documentary      |
| City     | rome   | paris        | venice   | prague       |

 